  "texts": [
    "Poor performances involved lesions of irregular shapes, in cases where the U-Net was unable to delineate definite boundaries.",
    "This was particularly evident in cases with complex tissue structures or low contrast between cancerous and non-cancerous regions.",
    "The proposed PolynetDWTCADx framework has high potentiality in real-world applications for clinical purposes, especially in the detection and treatment planning of colorectal cancer.",
    "With the incorporation of CNNs that capture robust features, DWT to enrich refinement in spatial-frequency features, and U-Net for precise segmentation, the framework demonstrates a dual capability in the detection and localization of cancerous tissues with high accuracy.",
    "This could integrate into existing colonoscopy systems to perform realtime assistance for highlighting potential cancerous regions during a procedure and helping physicians choose areas for biopsy or resection."
